{"attributes":{"title":"Consolidation outcome over time","description":"consolidation_attempt_recorded outcomes (success/extraction_returned_fallback/budget_denied) over time, 90d/full history. Replaces the original \"Dead-letter rate\" panel, which was mislabeled -- dead_letter is not a real outcome value this event ever emits; the real signal it queried was extraction_returned_fallback. Critical timeline finding, verified against live ES weekly buckets: week of 2026-04-27 was 99.7% fallback (702/704, an acute incident), week of 05-04 shifted to 100% budget_denied/success (0 fallback), a two-week gap (05-11 to 05-18) had zero attempts, and every week since 2026-05-25 (5+ consecutive weeks) has been 100% success. A time-collapsed aggregate (46.3% fallback all-time) would misleadingly read as an active crisis; the time axis is what makes current health legible.","visualizationType":"lnsXY","state":{"visualization":{"legend":{"isVisible":true,"position":"right"},"valueLabels":"hide","fittingFunction":"Linear","axisTitlesVisibilitySettings":{"x":true,"yLeft":true,"yRight":true},"tickLabelsVisibilitySettings":{"x":true,"yLeft":true,"yRight":true},"labelsOrientation":{"x":0,"yLeft":0,"yRight":0},"gridlinesVisibilitySettings":{"x":true,"yLeft":true,"yRight":true},"preferredSeriesType":"bar_stacked","layers":[{"layerId":"bf483515-73d1-4ba8-8032-463e88944a6d","accessors":["7675cc5f-aee4-40f5-a3a0-74e21f12ca3e"],"position":"top","seriesType":"bar_stacked","showGridlines":false,"layerType":"data","colorMapping":{"assignments":[],"specialAssignments":[{"rules":[{"type":"other"}],"color":{"type":"loop"},"touched":false}],"paletteId":"default","colorMode":{"type":"categorical"}},"xAccessor":"7c9d0477-4ccf-4bdb-af29-816583d6044d","splitAccessor":"3452e8aa-d049-4006-a5a3-60d3ea16a700"}]},"query":{"query":"event_type: \"consolidation_attempt_recorded\"","language":"kuery"},"filters":[],"datasourceStates":{"formBased":{"layers":{"bf483515-73d1-4ba8-8032-463e88944a6d":{"columns":{"34