{"attributes":{"description":"Extraction/consolidation health -- retry and failure rates for entity-extraction consolidation attempts (ADR-0065 / FRE-307), 90d default/full history. The original \"Dead-letter rate\" panel was mislabeled (dead_letter is not a real outcome value) and, as a role-only breakdown with no time axis, would misleadingly present a resolved 2026-04-27 incident as an ongoing 46% failure rate. Rebuilt around a time-axis outcome panel so current health (100% success for 5+ weeks) is legible alongside the historical totals. Kept the denial-reason panel (cap_exceeded is 100% of budget denials) and the attempts-to-success panel (median=1, p99=12), dropping the original per-role split since role is always entity_extraction.","kibanaSavedObjectMeta":{"searchSourceJSON":"{\"query\":{\"language\":\"kuery\",\"query\":\"\"},\"filter\":[]}"},"optionsJSON":"{\"hidePanelTitles\":false,\"useMargins\":true}","panelsJSON":"[{\"embeddableConfig\":{\"enhancements\":{}},\"gridData\":{\"h\":15,\"i\":\"panel-1\",\"w\":48,\"x\":0,\"y\":0},\"panelIndex\":\"panel-1\",\"panelRefName\":\"panel_0\",\"title\":\"Consolidation outcome over time\",\"type\":\"lens\",\"version\":\"8.9.0\"},{\"embeddableConfig\":{\"enhancements\":{}},\"gridData\":{\"h\":15,\"i\":\"panel-2\",\"w\":24,\"x\":0,\"y\":15},\"panelIndex\":\"panel-2\",\"panelRefName\":\"panel_1\",\"title\":\"Consolidation outcome totals\",\"type\":\"lens\",\"version\":\"8.9.0\"},{\"embeddableConfig\":{\"enhancements\":{}},\"gridData\":{\"h\":15,\"i\":\"panel-3\",\"w\":24,\"x\":24,\"y\":15},\"panelIndex\":\"panel-3\",\"panelRefName\":\"panel_2\",\"title\":\"Top denial reason\",\"type\":\"lens\",\"version\":\"8.9.0\"},{\"embeddableConfig\":{\"enhancements\":{}},\"gridData\":{\"h\":15,\"i\":\"panel-4\",\"w\":48,\"x\":0,\"y\":30},\"panelIndex\":\"panel-4\",\"panelRefName\":\"panel_3\",\"title\":\"Median attempts to success\",\"type\":\"lens\",\"version\":\"8.9.0\"}]","timeFrom":"now-90d","timeRestore":true,"timeTo":"now","t